    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors have been assessed or documented as epistemic gaps. Achieved levels are below required levels for 7 of 13 factors; however, the assessment team records the outcome as Accepted pending resolution of identified gaps in subsequent model revisions. Monte Carlo UQ results are within acceptable bounds for the primary hemolysis QoI at the two validated operating points. Remaining gaps, including the use of pre-revision rheological data (dataVintage 2018-03-15 vs modelRevisionDate 2026-01-10), are noted for remediation.",
